laboratory_examinations.findings: Showed length-dependent sensorimotor axonal neuropathy in the right lower extremity.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: At age 54.7 years, repeat EMG confirmed length-dependent, axonal, sensorimotor peripheral neuropathy.
